original: Kellner, Sven Gustav, ingenjör. Ankarsrum, f. 8/9/93 i Gränna av folk-S’k:lär. A. G. K. o. Albertina Levin. G. m. Alma Johansson. Barn: Siv f. 24, Berit o. Mona 38. — Utex. fr. Norrköp. tekn. eiem :sk. 11. Ritare v. Husqvarna Vapenfabr. A-B 11-14, verkst ring. där 14-31, verkst xhef h. A-B Westeråsmaskiner i Morgongåva 31-42, numera driftsing. v. A-B Ankarsrums Bruk.
translated: Kellner, Sven Gustav, engineer. Born on September 8, 1893 in Gränna to a schoolteacher's family. Son of A. G. K. and Albertina Levin. Married to Alma Johansson in [year]. Children: Siv (born in 1924), Berit, and Mona (born in 1938). Graduated from Norrköping Technical School in 1911. Worked as a draftsman at Husqvarna Vapenfabrik AB from 1911 to 1914, then in various positions in the workshop until 1931. Became workshop manager at A-B Westeråsmaskiner in Morgongåva from 1931 to 1942, and currently holds the position of engineer at A-B Ankarsrums Bruk.
